\id 2TH - Toma Bible 
\h 2 Tesalonike 
\toc1 Pɔle Ná-Sɛʋɛi Velesiɛi É Teʋeni Tesalonike Nuiti Ma 
\toc2 2 Tesalonike 
\toc3 2Te 
\mt2 Pɔle Ná-Sɛʋɛi Velesiɛi  //  É Teʋeni 
\mt1 Tesalonike Nuiti Ma 
\imt1 Sɛʋɛi lɔɔzeizuʋɛ ma woo mɔungiti 
\ip Keelai Pɔle é Tesalonike nuiti ta-zɛʋɛi velesiɛi ɠɛai (\xt 1:1\xt*). É Tesalonike nuiti ta-zɛʋɛ mɔungi ɠɛɛni, su la ɠoozani é felesiɛi nii ɠɛ, kona ʋuulɔɔlugɔ maazu ɠila (51) kɛɠala leʋegai ma, Kilista zɔlɔɔga ʋoluma. Pɔle ɠɛni dɛ Kolɛnte siɛgi zu é niima zɛʋɛi ɠɛa la, é teʋe Tesalonike Egilisii ma, Egilisii nii é daaɠulani ná-keela ziɛi velesiɛi zu (\xt KKw 17:1-10\xt*). Bogɛ Keelaiti Kɛɛwotiiti ma zɛʋɛi zu ga Egilisii naa zu nuiti ti ɠɛni ga Zuifui tanigaani ta Gɛlɛkii ma mɔinmɔin. 
\ip Kɛɛʋɛ eɠɛ Tesalonike Egilisii wola ɠilini yeeɠɛɠala ɠaaɓelagiti ta-vai ʋa ta Kilista ʋaa laa velesiɛi, tɔɔzei Pɔle faa mɔinmɔin sɛʋɛʋɛ é lo naama vai ʋa ná-sɛʋɛiti su ti leʋegai Tesalonike nuiti ma. Tesalonike nuiti ta-zɛʋɛi velesiɛi ɠilazuʋɛ kpein ka ɓɔɛzu é lo yeeɠɛɠala ɠaaɓelagi ʋa. Pɔle ti wola lɛnɛni é lo faaʋaalalai ʋa. Nui ɠilagilagi pɛ maanɛɛʋɛ é botii ɠɛ kɔnɔgi zɔlɔɔ fai zu (\xt 3:6-10\xt*). 
\iot Unsosuʋɛ 
\io1 1. Pɔle tɔɔzeiʋɛ ga é ɓɔɠɔ lɛɛ, naa ʋoluma é siɛɲɔɠɔiti ɓalaa dɛɛ (\xt 1:1-2\xt*). 
\io1 2. É zɛba é GALA mama ta é GALA fali Tesalonike Egilisii ʋɛ (\xt 1:3-12\xt*). 
\io1 3. Gaaɠwɛsu felegɔi zu, Pɔle ɠa ɓɔɛzu miná é lo yeeɠɛɠala ɠaaɓelagiti ba (\xt 2:1-17).\xt* 
\io1 4. Kpɔɛʋɛ naa ʋolu, é lo faaʋaalalai ʋa, ta ʋelei fizɔgai la nu botii ɠɛ (\xt 3:1-15\xt*). 
\io1 5. Pɔle gaaɓelagɛ ga é ná-tuʋɔ gooi laazeeli Egilisii ma (\xt 3:16-18\xt*). 
\c 1  
\s1 Tuʋɔ gooiti 
\p  
\v 1 Nɛ̀i gè ga Pɔle, gá Silase, naa ʋɛɛ Timɔte ʋa, gá wo luʋɔsu, wɔi wo Egilisii zu Tesalonike taazuʋɛ, wo ga Ɠɛɛɠɛ GALA ta Maliɠii Yesu Kilista nɔnɔiti.  
\v 2 Ɠɛɛɠɛ GALA ta Maliɠii Yesu Kilista ti zaalai la wo ma, ti ziilɛigi ve wo ʋɛ. 
\s1 Tukpɔɠaaleʋe vai Kilista ʋa voloi ʋolu 
\p  
\v 3 Kɛ̀ɛleaiti, gi maanɛɛʋɛ gi mamagi ve GALA bɛ yeenɔpɛ wa-vaa zu, gaamazu naa zɔlegɛ, mazɔlɔɔ wa-ɠidaaleʋei ɠa liizu luɠɔma gola, nɛɛbɛi é wo yɔɠɔzu, naa ɠa liizu ga wɔɔlɔa.  
\v 4 Gá unbuzeɠei lɛɛzu wa-vaa zu GALA ná-Egilisiiti su, tɔɔzei ʋelei wo loni la kpaan, ta ʋelei wa-ɠidaaleʋei la wɔinzeɠemaiti ta kpɔlɔiti pɛ saama wo sɔlɔɔsu. 
\p  
\v 5 Kpɔlɔi nii ɠa é ga GALA ná-telebo tukpɔɠaaleʋei ma ʋoogi, naa ɠa é dɛɛzu ga wa zoloo GALA ná-masadai zɔlɔɔ fai ma, nii wo kpɔlɔi zɔlɔɔsu maaʋele ma.  
\v 6 Soloogɛ ga GALA ge kpɔlɔi zei naati zea, niiti ti wo ɓɔlɔ vai laazu wo ya.  
\v 7 Wɔiti wo kpɔlɔi zu, GALA ge dooɠogi ve wo ya, ta gá ɓɔɠɔi gi ya, siɛgi zu Maliɠii Yesu ɠulazu la kɛlɛma, é zeɠe geeɠɔlɔgi zu, ta ná-geezuɠeelaiti, zɛbɛ wolai ti ya.  
\v 8 Toɠa ʋa abuzogi zaama, ga é naati sala, niiti ti la GALA kwɛɛ, ti la ɠolozu Woo Niinɛ Ʋagɔi ʋɛ, é ʋilɛ de-Maliɠii Yesu ʋa.  
\v 9 Ta ti-zalai zɔlɔɔ ga ɠɔoɠɔ undaaʋiligi, ti maaɠooza, ti zeɠe Maliɠii ɠaazu, ti maaɠooza ná-zobogi ma lɛbiyai ʋa,  
\v 10 siɛgi zu é ʋaazu la naama voloi, ga é lɛbiyai zɔlɔɔ ná-nuiti zea, niiti ta ɠidaaleʋe ma. Wa ɠɛ naati saama niiti ta maawui, tɔɔzei wo ɠidaaleʋeni gá-zeele wooi ma, gi boni wo ma. 
\p  
\v 11 Naa ɠa é ba, gá GALA falizu wo ʋɛ yeenɔpɛ, nii a kɛ ada-ƓALAGI wo ɠɛʋele ɓɛtɛ, wo zoloo toligi ma, é bogai ga woye. Gá falizu ná-zɛbɛi zu, ga faa ʋagɔi nii pɛ wo wɔinɗai ga wo kɛ, é naa laazeeli wo ʋɛ ga pagɔ, é wa-ɠidaaleʋei ma ɠɛɛwotii ɠaavɔni,  
\v 12 naa ɠa a kɛ Maliɠii Yesu laaseigi lɛbiyai zɔlɔɔ wo maaʋele ma, wa ɓalaa wo lɛbiyai zɔlɔɔ tɔun maaʋele ma, eɠɛʋelei da-ƓALAGI ná-zaalai la, ta de-Maliɠii Yesu Kilista. 
\c 2  
\s1 Tɔ Koloɠolo Nui ná-fai 
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ̀ɛleaiti, nii é ga ade-Maliɠii Yesu Kilista ʋaa vai, ta ada-maaɓɔ fai tɔun koba, gá wo maanɛɛnɛzu,  
\v 2 à mina va bu, wo yii ʋa ɓɔlɔ, wo zasu ʋa ɓali ga wooi ta, ga Maliɠii ná-foloi zeelia. Kɛɛʋɛ eɠɛ nui ta boni wo ma, kɛai ma kulakɛlɛma vaiti bosu, ɓaa é ɗa tɛnɛgi wo, ɓaa tanisu ti boni wo ma ga gi sɛʋɛni gá-zɛʋɛi ta zu.  
\v 3 À mina va bu, nu nɔpɛ ge ʋa wo ɠaka pele nɔpɛ ma. Mazɔlɔɔ aisa naama voloi ʋa zeeli, kɛni pele ʋilɛgi ɠɛ mɔunpa, Tɔ Koloɠolo Nui ɠula kɛlɛma, zunui nii undaaʋiligi leveai ma.  
\v 4 Tɔ Koloɠolo Nui naa, nii é wuzeɠezu naati pɛ daalɔɠɔma, niiti ti lolisu ga galagiti, ɓaa nuɓusɛ a ti lɛbi, eyɛsu é li, é zei GALA sei ʋɛlɛi wu, é ɓɔɠɔ lɛ eɠɛ a ɠɛ ga GALA. 
\p  
\v 5 Wo-ɠi ge la su ɓaa, ga gè niima vaiti boni wo ma, siɛgi zu gè ɠɛni la dɛ wo ʋɔ bɛ?  
\v 6 Anɛɛ naa ʋe, wo suɠwɛɛ, nii é pele ɓesasu dɛ tuɠɔ, ga é mina ɠula kɛlɛma kɛni ná-yeeɠɛɠalai.  
\v 7 Tɔ Koloɠolo Nui ná-zobogi é botii ɠɛɛzu la dɔɔɠuzu, naa ɠa ɠula niina kɛlɛma, kɛlɛ kɛni zɔi é pele ɓesasu dɛ tuɠɔ, naa a ɲɛɛlɛna.  
\v 8 Názu Tɔ Koloɠolo Nui ɠa ɠula niina kɛlɛma. Maliɠii Yesu ɠa paa ga laa viilɛi, é koloɠolo ga ná-kulakɛlɛmai ma zezei.  
\v 9 Tɔ Koloɠolo Nui naa ɠa ʋa ga Setana ná-zɛbɛi, é ɗa zɛɛ laavɔɔ vaiti kɛ, ta zɛɛ maaɓɛlɛ vaiti pɛ.  
\v 10 Toɠa telebotalai ma zii pɛ kɛ ga é naati kaka, niiti ti undaaʋilisu. Ti undaa ɠa ʋili, tɔɔzei ti la yeezeini gaamai wu, ti ʋa nɛɛ ʋɛ, nii a la ti ɠizo.  
\v 11 Naa ɠa é ba, GALA ka kakagi ma zobo golai leʋe ti ma, nii a kɛ ti la zɛɛi la,  
\v 12 naa ɠa a kɛ, niiti kpein ti la ɠidaaleʋeni gaamai ma, kɛlɛ ti telebotalai nɛai ʋɛ, ti ʋeelala. 
\s1 Tesalonike nuiti ta-lo kpaangi 
\p  
\v 13 Kɛ̀ɛleaiti, wɔi wo nɛai Maliɠii ʋɛ, maanɛɛʋɛ yeenɔpɛ gɔun gi ɗa GALA mama wa-vaa zu. Mazɔlɔɔ GALA ge yiimazeɠeʋɛ ga woye kaite tɔɔzeizu mɔunpa, é wo ɠizo Zɛnvu Ɲadegai zaalai zu nii é wo ɲadesu, ta wa-ɠidaaleʋei maaʋele gaamai ma.  
\v 14 GALA ge wo loligɛ naa ma ga Woo Niinɛ Ʋagɔi maaʋele, gi daazeelini wo ma ga wo ade-Maliɠii Yesu Kilista ná-lɛbiyai zɔlɔɔ.  
\v 15 Deɠɛmu, kɛ̀ɛleaiti, à lo kpaan, wo kala gooiti so, niiti gi ti woni wo ma ga gi-laaʋɛ, ɓaa ga zɛʋɛi. 
\p  
\v 16 Ade-Ɠɛɛ GALA nii é ade wola nɛai ʋɛ, é ɠɔoɠɔ iɲɔdɔɔi ve ade ʋɛ ta kito pagɔi ga zaalai maaʋele, ta ade-Maliɠii Yesu Kilista ɓɔɠɔi  
\v 17 wo-yiiti daave ga iɲɔdɔɔi, é wo zɛbɛlɔ, wo ziɛ ga faa ʋagɔiti pɛ, kɛɛwotiiti su ta wo ɓɔɛ ʋeleiti su. 
\c 3  
\s1 Toligi é lo GALA falii ʋa 
\p  
\v 1 Kɛ̀ɛleaiti, gaaɓelagi ɠa ga: À GALA fali gi ʋɛ, ga Maliɠii laawooi li ga vazaga, é lɛbiyai zɔlɔɔ, eɠɛʋelei é ɠɛɛzu la wo ʋɔ bɛ.  
\v 2 À GALA fali ɓalaa ga é gi ɠizo faa ɲɔu ɠɛ nuiti ta suɲɔu nuiti ma, mazɔlɔɔ kidaaleʋei la ɛsɛ pɛ zea. 
\p  
\v 3 Kɛlɛ Maliɠii ɠa ga wooɠɛɠila nu. Toɠa wo zɛbɛlɔ, é wo makɛ ma ɲɔi ma.  
\v 4 Maliɠii naama ladalai veeʋɛ gi ya wa-vaa zu, ga fai niiti gi ɠɛai wo ti ɠɛ, wa naati kɛɛzu, ta wa yɛsu ti ɠɛɛzu. 
\p  
\v 5 Maliɠii lo wo-yiimaʋɛti tuɠɔ, ti laazeeli GALA ná-nɛɛbɛi zu faan, ta é ziilɔɔi ma zobogi ve wo ʋɛ ga Kilista ɠɛʋele faan. 
\s1 Botii ɠɛ ungi 
\p  
\v 6 Kɛ̀ɛleaiti, gá wo levezu, Maliɠii Yesu Kilista laaseigi zu, ga wo maaɠooza ɠɛɛɠɛloin kpein ba, niiti ti eteai ziɛzu dɔɔʋɛi zu, ti la ziɛzu ga kalagi naa, nii gi boni ga woye.  
\v 7 Wa ɓɔɠɔi wo suɠwɛɛ kpezekele, ʋelei wo maanɛai la wo ʋokɔɠɔ gi ma. Mazɔlɔɔ gi la ɠɛni zeini wo zaama ga dɔɔʋɛ vaa,  
\v 8 gi la ɠɛni vaani bu nu nɔpɛ ge ʋa gi ɠɔnɔkula ni gi la sɔngɔ veeni, kɛlɛ tɔun, gi kpɔlɔi ɠwɛɛni, ta gi botii ɠɛɛni folo ʋɛɛ kpidi ʋa, nii a kɛ gi mina ɠɛ ga kasɔ wo taɠila kpalaa unma.  
\v 9 É la ga ma zobo ka é la ɠɛni gi ʋɛ, kɛlɛ wɔin ɠɛni gi ma, ga gi poo fe wo ya, wa ɠɛ ziɛzu la.  
\v 10 Mazɔlɔɔ siɛgi zu gi ɠɛni la wo ʋɔ bɛ, gi niima levei veeni wo ya ga: «Zɔi nɔpɛ é la pɔ ga é botii ɠɛ, é mina daami wo.» 
\p  
\v 11 Tama gá mɛnisu ga, tanigaa ta wo zaama, ti ta-eteai ziɛzu dɔɔʋɛi zu, ti la faa nɔpɛ kɛɛzu, kɛni faazupui nɔ.  
\v 12 Gá ɓɔɛzu naama nui naati pɔ Maliɠii Yesu Kilista laaseigi zu, devei gi feezu, toɠa ga ti botii ɠɛ ziilɛigi zu, ti-zɔlɔɔ ganii ɠɛ ga ti-ɠɔnɔgi. 
\p  
\v 13 Wɔun wo letegi, kɛ̀ɛleaiti, à mina ɓɔlɔ ga faa ʋagɔi ɠɛɛ vai.  
\v 14 Ni nui ta la ɠɛ ziɛni ga kala gooi nii gi bosu wo ma niima zɛʋɛi zu, à ɠizɛ su, kpɔfaama nɔpɛ ge mina ɠɛ wo yɔɠɔzu, wa tiyagaani, naa ɠa a kɛ ti unfe.  
\v 15 À mina pɛtɛ ga wo zili nu, kɛlɛ à tɛnɛ eɠɛ ɠɛɛɠɛloun. 
\s1 Tuya loo vai ta tuʋɔ fai 
\p  
\v 16 Maliɠii nii é ziilɛigi veezu, naa ɓɔɠɔi ziilɛigi ve wo ʋɛ mɛtu fai pɛ su. Maliɠii yɛ wo pɛ wo ʋa. 
\p  
\v 17 Nà Pɔle, nà ɓɔɠɔi zèeʋogi ɠa gè wo luʋɔsu da. Naa ɠa é ga zèeʋogi nà-sɛʋɛiti pɛ su, zekana nà ɗa sɛʋɛ la. 
\p  
\v 18 De-Maliɠii Yesu Kilista ná-zaalai yɛ wo pɛ wo ʋa.